{"word":"Ahaz","slug":"ahaz","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahaz</b> <a href=\"#/H271\">H271</a> <br/> 1. King of Judah, son and successor of Jotham<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=38'>2Ki 15:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=1'>2Ki 16:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=27&verse=9'>2Ch 27:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=1'>2Ch 28:1</a> <br/> - Idolatrous abominations of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=4'>2Ki 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=4'>2Ch 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=25'>2Ch 28:25</a> <br/> - Kingdom of, invaded by the kings of Syria and Samaria,<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=6'>2Ki 16:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=8'>2Ch 28:8</a> <br/> - Robs the temple to purchase aid from the king of Assyria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=9'>2Ki 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=18'>2Ki 16:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=21'>2Ch 28:21</a> <br/> - Visits Damascus, obtains a novel pattern of an altar, which he substitutes for the altar in the temple in Jerusalem, and otherwise perverts the forms of worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=16'>2Ki 16:16</a> <br/> - Sundial of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=11'>2Ki 20:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=8'>Isa 38:8</a> <br/> - Prophets in the reign of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=1'>Isa 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=1'>Hos 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=1&verse=1'>Mic 1:1</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=25'>Isa 7:25</a> <br/> - Succeeded by Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=20'>2Ki 16:20</a> <br/> 2. Son of Micah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=35'>1Ch 8:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=42'>1Ch 9:42</a>"}]}